{"tid":456172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逼狗拿筆學英文 男子虐狗拍片捱轟","createTime":"2017-11-02T17:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T17:21:26.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8361be18228e67d8601a3bca966dcf91cd32b2cf","tid":456172,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tqQ.ep3lK3zly3G9ZyEb5w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-11-02/7dcdab00-bfa1-11e7-acec-95fe40189646__2017110214571537614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtqQ.ep3lK3zly3G9ZyEb5w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fl.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-11-02%2F7dcdab00-bfa1-11e7-acec-95fe40189646__2017110214571537614.jpg&h=639ed673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】網上近日瘋傳一段令人髮指的短片，一個男人抓著一隻狗的前腳，一邊說「A for apple，B for ball」，還逼狗隻學英文、寫單字，只要狗不專心轉頭就立即「摑牠一巴」，而且畫面外傳來竊笑聲音，最後狗隻懷疑受不住太痛逃走。<br />\n<br />\n該短片中，男子將筆插在狗爪，然後開始虐待，要狗學習在筆記本寫字，但狗不是人，根本不知道在做什麼，一直張望觀察四周，男子發怒打牠，起初狗隻還想反抗，露齒想作出攻擊，但該男子更大力的打，最後逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n網友憤怒地說片中人和拍片者根本不尊重生命，反問是否「讓我抓著你學中文，呼吸一次打一次！」、「這根本不是人，我要是狗我就立刻撕爛他的喉嚨」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E9%80%BC%E7%8B%97%E6%8B%BF%E7%AD%86%E5%AD%B8%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%99%90%E7%8B%97%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F-065200644.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E9%2580%25BC%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%258B%25BF%25E7%25AD%2586%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2599%2590%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%258D%25B1%25E8%25BD%259F-065200644.html&d=NcqQRCZ2A5PjWhcJ3Pxkfk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2fff2e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E9%80%BC%E7%8B%97%E6%8B%BF%E7%AD%86%E5%AD%B8%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%99%90%E7%8B%97%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F-065200644.html</a>"}]}